---
title: Sticky Chermoula Beef & Veggie Couscous with Baby Leaves, Halloumi & Yoghurt
description: Prepare for a flavour adventure, where sweet apricot meets herbaceous and mildly spicy chermoula in a bold harmony that will dazzle your tastebuds! Tender beef & halloumi takes on these flavours with ease, and is perfectly balanced with a colourful veggie couscous and a cooling dollop of yoghurt.
